    "summary": "The user engages the assistant in a discussion about linguistic competence, presenting two texts: one in standard academic English and one in a vernacular dialect. The user challenges the assistant's initial prioritization of the formal text, questioning whether this preference constitutes a bias that reinforces exclusionary cultural norms in professional settings.",
